{"tid":2464271,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"尷尬！港建制派團體到H＆M遞信嗆道歉 卻被拍到腳穿NIKE","createTime":"2021-03-27T10:33:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-27T10:43:46.000Z","uid":276273,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f6a80eba9cca60cc9b5ea98957654111ae161081","tid":2464271,"uid":276273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T10:33:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3480845\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3480845&d=jrWVSpMJYTM9%2F%2BTkK0Hr37vH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=2109c6e9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3480845&h=495bc094\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3480845</a><br />\n<br />\n2021/03/27 14:57  <br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕「拒用新疆棉」風波持續延燒，除了不少藝人更紛紛切割丶解除合作，也有香港政治人物選邊站，香港建制派一向被視為親中勢力，當中團體「公民力量」也對涉及這次風波的企業H＆M發出譴責，甚至到辦公室請願嗆道歉，不過卻被港媒拍到團體成員腳上穿的是中國網友也抵制的NIKE鞋子，引來網友嘲諷。<br />\n多家品牌「拒用新疆棉」過去的公告被共青團、中共官媒挖出，中國國內掀起抵制風潮，多名藝人及經紀公司更是紛紛跳船表態站邊，其中不乏許光漢、彭于晏等台灣藝人，讓粉絲大失所望。<br />\n除了為了不和市場過不去而表態的藝人，也有政治人物或是公民團體為了「挺中」，表態站邊嗆H＆M，香港建制派團體「公民力量」李梓敬一行人稍早高舉「我是中國人，我用新疆棉」的標語，至香港H＆M尖沙嘴辦公室遞信請願，痛批H＆M抹黑中國，要求道歉。<br />\n不過《立場新聞》卻發現，雖然李梓敬穿的是中國品牌飛躍（Feiyue）的白鞋，但團體另一成員則穿上同樣被捲入這次風波的NIKE品牌鞋款，引來不少網友訕笑，直呼「反正最後都會是搬石頭砸自己的腳」、「現場燒掉鞋子！」"},{"pid":"ed1a170f02f37f4dd868ba32d4a79ae119e3f738","tid":2464271,"uid":124372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T10:34:26.000Z","msg":"霞姨"},{"pid":"1aa13040dd64050d3529aadee648ee1449e39325","tid":2464271,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T10:37:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0af63229ed7e66774b93058f70dd53d390cfd9ee","tid":2464271,"uid":290118,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T10:38:32.000Z","msg":"呢班忠誠的廢物柒到台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"795b24125f6a4676de4a79e9cf5b56724e184679","tid":2464271,"uid":61653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T10:39:13.000Z","msg":"文革2.0<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"559cea31e2c531dd6abbe8864802f0c6c406d6f8","tid":2464271,"uid":357030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T10:39:19.000Z","msg":"柒到去台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4e058bae4743c383f5af866bf6a7697a90c6d83","tid":2464271,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T10:41:29.000Z","msg":"又唔忠誠又廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7659c2aeae4227389b9bf911452c2349ca568d2","tid":2464271,"uid":259901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T10:43:46.000Z","msg":"搬起nike砸自己隻腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}